    "description": "Juki Corporation manufactures and sells industrial and household sewing machines, and industrial equipment in Japan, China, India, rest of Asia, the Americas, Europe, and internationally. The company operates through Sewing Business; and Industrial Equipment Business segments. It offers industrial sewing machines for sewing apparel products, underwear, sportswear, shoes, bags, indoor furniture, daily commodities, car interior components, and hobby and amusement items; household sewing machines, professional sewing machines, and compact overlock sewing machines; and surface mounting technology (SMT) related equipment that are used primarily to mount electronic components, such as IC chips, semiconductors, and capacitors on electronic circuit boards. The company is also involved in the contract development and manufacturing business; and provides automated warehouse solutions. In addition, it provides smart solutions for sewing factories and circuit boards manufacturing factories. Juki Corporation was founded in 1938 and is headquartered in Tama, Japan."
